name: HENMON - Limited Edition
description:
Say hello to Henmon! Henmon wants to celebrate hicetnunc.xyz's 500k event with you! This card is only available for this occasion and waiting to get collected by you, to contribute to HEN's success of 500.000 minted OBJKTs. Help Henmon advance to 1.000.000, soon to be the number one! 

This card is a one time only release for this special event and available in limited editions of 500. Congratulations to HEN and all artists and developers involved to make this place feel better each day!

by APESTA
